data.description: Nestled in a great location, this move-in ready multi-split-level home offers the perfect blend of convenience and comfort. It has an updated kitchen with a stainless steel dishwasher and an attached 2-car garage for convenience and storage. Also, enjoy outdoor living at its finest with a generously sized front and backyard. Whether it's hosting gatherings, gardening, or simply unwinding in the open air, this home offers versatile outdoor spaces to suit your lifestyle. Residents have easy access to parks, shopping centers, entertainment venues, and diverse dining options. Commuting to Downtown Atlanta or Downtown Decatur is a breeze, making this home an ideal choice for urban dwellers. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this gem your own. Schedule a showing today. This home is ready for you to make it your own.
